---
import LibraryLayout from "../layouts/LibraryLayout.astro";
---

<LibraryLayout
  title="せおはやみ ── 叡智の星海"
  description="盲目の主人公せおはやみが「叡智の星海」で、思想が人格化した住人たちに、人の業を自由に訊く哲学アンソロジー。駅間で読める短い会話劇。"
  bgImage="promotional/cast/shadow-library-reading-guide.webp"
  bgPosition="50% 38%"
  bgPositionMobile="50% 18%"
>
  <section class="th-cover th-cover--home">
    <div
      class="th-cover__image"
      aria-hidden="true"
      style="--th-cover-image: url('/images/promotional/cast/shadow-library-cast.webp');"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/promotional/cast/shadow-library-cast.webp"
        alt=""
        width="1672"
        height="941"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="th-cover__copy th-glow">
      <p class="th-cover__issue">叡智の星海</p>
      <h1 class="sr-only">せおはやみ</h1>
      <img
        src="/images/logo/theo-logo.webp"
        alt=""
        class="th-cover__logo"
        width="1200"
        height="472"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <p class="th-cover__tagline">人の業を、時を超えた知性に訊く</p>
      <nav class="th-cover__nav" aria-label="扉">
        <a href="/story" class="th-link-button th-link-button--primary no-underline">本編を読む</a>
        <a href="/anthology" class="th-link-button no-underline">自由行動へ</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pb-14">
    <section class="th-magazine-section th-magazine-section--home-guide">
      <p class="th-magazine-section__folio">001 / Reading Guide</p>
      <h2>一駅ぶんの問いを、ひとり選ぶ。</h2>
      <p>
        駅と駅のあいだで読める、小さな会話劇です。長編ゲームではありません。
        「消えるのが怖い」「人がうらやましい」「損得で動いてしまう」――誰もが抱える業を、
        思想が人格化した住人たちに、好きな組み合わせで尋ねてください。
      </p>
      <nav class="th-path-tree" aria-label="読み方">
        <a href="/story" class="th-path-tree__item th-path-tree__item--main">
          <span class="th-path-tree__label">本編</span>
          <span class="th-path-tree__text">物語を辿る</span>
        </a>
        <div class="th-path-tree__branch" aria-label="自由行動">
          <p class="th-path-tree__label">じっくり読む時間がないときは</p>
          <p class="th-path-tree__text">自由行動</p>
          <div class="th-path-tree__children">
            <a href="/anthology" class="th-path-tree__item">
              <span class="th-path-tree__label">住人から</span>
              <span class="th-path-tree__text">顔を見て選ぶ</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/themes" class="th-path-tree__item">
              <span class="th-path-tree__label">業から</span>
              <span class="th-path-tree__text">悩みから選ぶ</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/tea-time" class="th-path-tree__item">
          <span class="th-path-tree__label">004</span>
          <span class="th-path-tree__text">けふのティータイム</span>
        </a>
      </nav>
    </section>
  </div>
</LibraryLayout>
